cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with image segmentation using deep learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model also involves global information aggregation, which is a technique used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model is based on 3D U-Net, which is a neural network architecture commonly used in medical image analysis (cs.NE). Finally, the paper specifically focuses on multimodality isointense infant brain MR image segmentation, which falls under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
